  clientName: Merchant Clara
  jobDescription: I need a sturdy bridge to transport my heavy crate of iron tools
    across the gorge. Do not let it fall!
  budget: 5000
  cargoWeight: 500
  offerDialogue:
    name: Merchant Clara
    sentences:
    - Hello, builder. I need your help.
    - The bridge across has collapsed, and I need to deliver a crate of iron tools
      to the settlement on the other side.
    - "The crate weighs 500kg, so the bridge must be strong and stable. It can\u2019t
      be weak or unstable."
    - My budget is $4000 for materials. Build a solid bridge and carry the crate
      safely to the delivery area. Can you take this job?
